2.title: Docker Cheat Sheet
2.content: Docker Cheat Sheet . How to: . list images . docker images . remove an image . docker rmi "name or ID" . see all containers . docker -ps -a . run a container . docker run -d "name or ID" . restart a container . docker restart "name or ID" . stop a container . docker stop "name or ID" . remove a container . docker rm "name or ID" .
